{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blood &amp; Chaos\u00a0is a <strong>roguelike RPG</strong> that puts you in command of a  party of adventurers. <br>Build a team of up to six unique heroes, each with their own skills and abilities, and lead them through a perilous, ever-changing world. Strategize, adapt, and overcome challenging turn-based battles as you explore vibrant cities, uncover hidden quests, and delve into deadly dungeons.<br>Will your fellowship rise to become legends, or will they be consumed by the chaos?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628880/extras/separator.png?t=1739204984\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build Your Party</strong>: Create your party of up to 6 heroes, each with \u00a0unique skills and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tactical Turn-Based Combat:</strong>\u00a0<strong>:</strong>\u00a0Engage in challenging battles where every move counts. Position your heroes wisely, exploit enemy weaknesses, and unleash powerful spells and abilities to turn the tide of battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2628880/extras/videogif_1.gif?t=1739204984\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Dynamic World of Contrasts:</strong>\u00a0Explore a richly detailed medieval fantasy world where beauty and danger coexist. From bustling cities to cursed ruins, every location tells a story of light and shadow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Epic Quests:</strong> Legends speak of a war that nearly consumed the world. Now, remnants of that battle stir once more. What role will you play in the next chapter?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Nostalgic Yet Modern:</strong>\u00a0A love letter to '80